<div n="monument" type="description">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>
A <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"><rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft</rs> without moulding (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">1.04</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.44</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.45</measure>); complete, but worn along the upper edge, and pierced for later use as a <rs type="objectType">well-head</rs>.</p>
</div>

<div n="text" type="description">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>
Inscribed on the face; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>

<div n="letters" type="description">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p>
ll.1-2, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>; ll.3-5, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.022</measure>.  Ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign>, l.2; <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign>, l.3.</p>
</div>

<div n="date" type="description">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0260" exact="both" notBefore="0253">A.D. 253-260</date>
(<rs type="criteria">reign</rs>).</p>
</div>

